h3 Intro

p.
  This plugin provides the handling of showing a modal.
  See the modal block for further information.

h3 Usage

p Activate the functionality with the data-* API

.highlight
  pre.highlight__listing.hljs: code.js
    :highlight
      <a data-modal="#myModal" ></a>

p Activate the functionality with JavaScript:

.highlight
  pre.highlight__listing.hljs: code.js
    :highlight
      $('#myModal').modal(options)

